          R. and Malik, Rohit and Feng, Felix and Chinnaiyan, Arul M. 
          and Collins, Colin C. and Sahinalp, S. Cenk and Backofen, 
          Rolf},
title = {{MechRNA}: prediction of {lncRNA} mechanisms from 
